name: Hurry-Scurry
description:
Welcome to the new competitive Hurry-Scurry game. Take part in a big race against real living people from all over the world, come to the finish line first and snatch victory from under the noses of your opponents. Run different ways on colorful levels, find the shortest ones - this will help you to reach the finish line first. Unlock really great costumes to be the coolest one in the match.
Run, jump and win!
